w features of nanoparticle scattering\nsuch as the spectral correlation and temporal response of light scattered by\nnano scatterers, including Mie spheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 11:35:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 03:22:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
