$ even inside a protoplanetary disk, and\ntherefore, can be used to trace material evolution in disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 14:14:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 May 2022 16:35:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-06"}
