\nnetwork performance. Our results indicate that, with a proper switching method,\nthe joint implementation of FSO/THz links, improves the rate/reliability of the\nbackhaul links with limited switching overhead.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 15:01:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 07:34:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 17:36:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-14"}
