 break-out of the engine-powered shock from the\nejecta into the preceding wind. The model requires total energetics of just few\n$\\times 10^{50}$ ergs, slightly above the observed X-rays. We predict that the\nsystem is hydrogen poor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 15:22:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2022 01:38:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2022 14:24:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 17 Jun 2022 12:00:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
